4 x z9 mini = 4096$ - 95$ for 1 psu because 1 psu is for 2 z9mini  =~4000$ for 60/khs and 1200watt
so 4 x z9mini are better than a 1 innosilicon with +500$ less than innosilicon, +10 k/h that is +576,22â‚¬ 
(1 K/s = 4000/60 = 66$ x 10K/h = 660$  => 576,22â‚¬  )

electricity in italy is about 0,30 cent so 500 watt a day is about 3,6â‚¬
436,53â‚¬ + 576,22 = 1012,75 / 3.6â‚¬ day =  â‚¬ 281days 

after 281 days innosilicon is better than z9 mini
